Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:38.11,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,The "Confirm Maintenance on the Command Transmission Line for Direct Communication with Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:42.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,in the Case of a High-Level Emergency Situation" mission. {honei chokutsuu koudo kinkyuu hijyou jitai wo shirei tentatsu kaisen hoshu kakunin ninmu. wow that sucked. she groups all of her...syllables? incorrect here so it's like...him yna meis~ (hi my name is) it's like...impossible to get the first time around. idk if you want to try to convey that in the english}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:44.89,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's one amazing name, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.22,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,It's an extremely important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:51.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,The sort which, should you fail, it's possible that the entire troop would be punished for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:55.89,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the situation, the first series of alerts would be announced,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:59.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,and all divisions in the area would be placed on emergency standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:04.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really.  It truly is a hugely important responsibility, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,W-What kind of mission is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:09.54,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Telephone duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.50,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:21.97,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,You know that this phone is a hotline to Headquarters at the capital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:24.22,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Up til now, has it ever rung before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.09,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,No, it hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.52,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  Thankfully it never has.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:28.93,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But if it did—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:31.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Right.  When it does ring, it's bothersome,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:34.61,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,but if it didn't ring when necessary, that would be even worse, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:39.53,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, every six months, we perform a check to test whether the line is properly connected or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.28,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,And that's called...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:42.86,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,T-The... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:45.03,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, be sure to remember it properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:48.79,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Communication with Headquarters in Emergency... what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:52.96,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's the Direct Communication with Headquarters in a High-Level... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:57.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,The "Confirm Maintenance on the Command Transmission Line for Direct Communication with Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:04:00.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,in the Case of a High-Level Emergency Situation" mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:01.92,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Like so!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.55,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!  Yes, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.22,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow {\i1}me{\i0} to accept that mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:12.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to try speaking on the telephone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.22,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really that exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:18.73,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,The basic arrangement is the same as the {\i1}Takemikazuchi{\i0}'s intercom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:20.59,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Just because the distance is a little further...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.36,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:25.74,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to speak with people so far away... it's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:31.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true that it is a curious feeling, to speak with someone you can't see at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.96,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but once you get used to it, it's nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:39.59,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,However, the only troublesome thing is that we don't know when they will call today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.96,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, would you still like to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:42.33,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:47.34,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,All right.  Then you're to stick to the phone for the entire day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:05:00.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,This is the 1121st stronghold of the Helvetian Army.  Private Second Class Sorami Kanata speaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:07.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,And then, when the call is finished, you return the receiver back to the same place it was in before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:08.05,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:50.87,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Phy-Phy—!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:53.27,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's because you're just too cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.91,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Phylicia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,What are you {\i1}doing{\i0}?  Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.08,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.21,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,The steam train's leaving. {steam train apparently, not the regular word for train}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.21,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,"Steam train"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:06.59,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,I have some documents that must be rushed to Headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:09.40,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,And Krause-san isn't coming until next week, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:11.26,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:14.37,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave telephone duty firmly in your care, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:14.93,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.78,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,If it actually rings, at worst,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:22.35,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,it's possible for them to think that we've been attacked instead.  So make sure you don't mess up! {saiyaku koko ga kougeki saretatte handan sareru koto mo arundakara}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.35,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:47.58,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:49.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:50.26,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.09,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,A-Absolutely have {\i1}not{\i0} been sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:55.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:57.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,In the hangar again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:02.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:05.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,So, Kanata, what do you want to eat for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:07.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:10.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.  It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.07,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:18.14,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why is it that when it's my turn to make food, both you and Kureha try to keep me from doing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:22.36,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,You know, before you two got here, I did it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:24.59,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.39,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,The taste shouldn't be that bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:30.72,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, that's true, the taste isn't as bad as its loo—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.20,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,No!  I-I mean, it has a very clear, distinct taste that's totally wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:36.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:41.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Then today, I'll put in even more effort than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, is there anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.40,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.24,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, Naomi-san is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:52.19,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:56.45,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But I need to stay by the phone or else!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.77,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys have a guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:02.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.  There's no helping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.21,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!  I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:12.78,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to eat sandwiches with pieces of the cutting board mixed in again, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:17.35,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.39,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,It's apple cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:23.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly they're home-brewed from where we get our wholesale apple juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:28.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Then these are related to the calvados we have here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:29.54,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:34.33,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see... the secret's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:35.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.46,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,As a payment, two bottles would be good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:45.10,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Oh, yes, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.08,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,"Payment"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:50.09,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,There's going to be a merchant guild's meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:54.77,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for accommodating us so often{i.e. being flexible and letting them get away with stuff}, it's become tradition to give them a little something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:55.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:56.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:58.98,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:02.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Those girls have always tried their hardest to hide that this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you find out? {lit: why was the secret exposed?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.49,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:12.36,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a chance, I'll tell you some time in the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:17.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,575)}Anyway, Naomi-san, would you like to have lunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:19.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that I should go, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:24.80,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Look here, it seems that everyone wants to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:28.59,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,an explanation from the military about the news in this week's paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:29.52,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,"News"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:33.16,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,About how the armistice agreement meetings have been hitting some rough patches. {kyuusen kyoutei no kaigi ga nankou shiterutte yatsu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:35.22,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:39.92,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,They're working out details for reparation amounts and delineation lines for territory. {baishoukin no gaku ya ryoudo no senbiki wo chimachima}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:42.16,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Even though things like these always drag on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:47.99,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the real intention of the old guys at the guild is probably only to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:52.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, ever since you played one of the fire maidens at the water-pouring festival{did we have a name for this? if we did, please switch to that name ^^"},
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.39,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,your fanbase has been growing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.72,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,How irritating.  Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:03.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,So, as you can see, somehow it seems I have no choice but to show up at this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.85,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Even I'm a bastion maiden now, body and soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:08.91,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I will carry out this mission on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:11.93,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.  I'll leave things in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:12.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:19.60,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, I'll give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine, so I'm sorry it's so old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:26.49,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,This is... a trumpet...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:29.99,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful, wonderful, wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:31.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:35.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Your trumpet-playing has gotten much better, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.95,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,It's your reward for working so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:40.77,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,And also, if you have that, you should be able to stay awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:55.80,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Um... this is a C... D, E, F, G...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:58.09,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:16.85,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess summer's just about over...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:27.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Ilya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:34.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I might've drunk a little too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.65,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-chan?  Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.47,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining!  The laundry's going to get soaked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:52.21,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,The courtyard is within scope of the mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:01.48,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:02.92,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:05.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,You really saved me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:27.03,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0025,,It's fine.  I'm simply glad that your laundry is safe. {this sentence is so funny xD}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:28.66,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0025,,Yeah, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:33.57,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0025,,I-I'm sorry!  Asking for help out of the blue like that—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0025,,Oh, please don't be bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:38.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0025,,I apologize as well, for coming over to visit so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:41.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0025,,I must return to Treize tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0025,,and so I've come to bid my farewells. {his language is through the roof polite}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:46.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0025,,Y-You're too kin—{she says it's too polite, but it's cut off =/}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.85,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there's no need to say goodbye to soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:52.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, Seiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:56.29,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that this child has been disrespectful to the people at this base,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:13:00.43,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,so I also thought to apologize for that, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:02.46,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:04.56,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,They're out at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:08.09,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,The black-haired one, also?  Rio-san, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:08.97,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:12.34,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I would have liked— {sketchy sounding? perhaps make it sound less sketch?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.98,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Is this book... yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, what is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.08,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,A trumpet book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:21.08,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I received it from Rio-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:24.44,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:25.95,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:29.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, no, please excuse me.  I was merely speaking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, are you here all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.09,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:34.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It's the, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:39.56,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,"Confirm Maintenance on the Command Transmission Line for Direct Communication with Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:44.26,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,in the Case of a High-Level Emergency Situation" mission! {she still says it wrong}{mid, make sure I split this right, mid^^; -yuuri}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:51.40,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Then I presume you're waiting for this to ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:57.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But this is my first time using one and I'm sort of nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:01.29,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just wondering if I can say what I need to say properly, and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:03.22,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you like to practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:04.35,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:11.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Then Yumina-san has also gone to the guild meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:16.74,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  She's attending to get donations from the people at the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.73,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:23.36,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.52,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:25.80,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-kun, you drink up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:30.59,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll drink it, but you won't win me over with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,What are you making?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.27,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio, Seiya, do you two know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:43.76,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,A phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.45,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:56.73,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's a phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:15:01.14,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing how the children enjoy it, I make them from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:02.47,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, Seiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:03.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:06.21,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,A phone, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.47,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:13.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:17.47,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!  This is amazing, Seiya-kun!  I can hear you loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:21.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,That's not right!  When you answer the phone, you say\N "Hello" first.  That's a rule when using the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:24.32,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.30,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:31.44,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing.  Really amazing!  I can really hear his voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:34.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be all right to practice with that then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:34.52,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.58,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Um... this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.53,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:47.18,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,This is the 1121st stronghold of the Helvetian Army.  Private Second Class Sorami Kanata speaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.54,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:52.54,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am honored to receive this phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.80,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,And, uh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:59.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ms. Birdie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:00.92,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.03,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,No, stop, Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.28,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.79,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,The phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,{so extra x.x}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,{HAHAHAHA}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:44.34,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, are the priest and children—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:11.52,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the gods above!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.76,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:17.99,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,You were supposed to come here and offer thanks and apologies for all that has happened recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:20.79,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,and instead you end up playing around and causing trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,{nante iu koto desu ka. ima made no orei to owabi ni goasatsu ni kita hazu nano ni asonde gomeiwaku wo kakesuru nante}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:23.73,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no dinner tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:25.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Children,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.44,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,For me, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.57,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's okay now.  Thanks for helping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,But your clothes are drenched...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.16,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.  I have a change of...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:45.66,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,I have a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:54.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,This is... embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:58.60,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how dazzling you look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:03.32,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Still, thanks, Yumina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:05.34,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to wash and return these clothes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:07.09,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm giving them to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.31,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,They're too big for the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:15.45,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't think of anyone else who would look as good in them as you do, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Will you still play with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:22.85,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.74,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-kun, you come back again soon too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:27.13,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:36.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,I-If I'm free, I'll come over and play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:38.88,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:42.03,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,May there be countless blessings upon you all. {it is plural. and it should be the same line that yumina used in ep 3 when kanata got sick - idk if you changed it}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:45.55,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:52.22,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,All right, time for clean up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:56.10,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot, I need to use the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:32.99,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It'll leak...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:28.45,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!!{aww haha}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, those old guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.54,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kana—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:43.26,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, please!  Save... me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:45.76,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:48.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:52.30,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It'll leak out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:53.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:55.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:57.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:00.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Was she holding it in the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:03.61,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know whether to call that being stupid or being honest to a fault... {honesty /i might have one word wrong here}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:12.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.89,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm... fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:17.39,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:21.55,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Not... possible!  I can't move at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:24.89,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Her timing really sucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:33.60,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is the 1121st Platoon of the Helvetian Army.  Sergeant Major Rio Kazumiya speaking. {she says rio kazumiya btw, not the other way around}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.39,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:41.36,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that we were confirming your line, and so I insisted...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:42.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:45.63,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not running!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:47.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:50.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,You just haven't forgiven me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:53.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,After all this time, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:58.93,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you... I ask you to save this country, to save Helvetia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:03.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:08.22,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-chan, don't tell me you've been... since this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:11.43,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  I sleep well on the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:13.08,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:17.31,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,We're ho—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:21.88,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!  How cute you look, Kana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:24.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,More like, what are you two doing here in the hallway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:27.88,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata fell over and can't stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:28.88,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Is she hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:32.20,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Then hurry and stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:37.96,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, I guess there's no helping it then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:39.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Spoiled darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:42.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,No... stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.47,0:22:44.73,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Here we...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:48.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
